license: MIT
abstract: >
  Code and datasets for comparing three activation-steering methods (GCS, AGCS, KCS)
  for controlling the emotional tone of instruction-tuned LLMs at inference time,
  without any parameter updates. Evaluated across five open-weight models and five
  target emotions using an LLM-as-a-Judge protocol.
